videos.description: In transition,  P.J. Thompson throws it to Isaac Haas who slams down the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Purdue's Haas throws it down

videos.description: Sam Hauser bounces passes it to Theo John who hits a reverse.
videos.headline: John finishes with a reverse layup

videos.description: Boilermakers' Andrew Rowsey blocks Golden Eagles' Carsen Edwards shot, and gets his shot attempt swatted away from Edwards.
videos.headline: Back-to-back blocks by Purdue and Marquette

videos.description: Golden Eagles' Andrew Rowsey quickly throws it to Markus Howard who hits a three-pointer.
videos.headline: Marquette's Howard drains 3-pointer

videos.description: Marquette's Andrew Rowsey draws foul on 3-pointer and makes his free throw.
videos.headline: Rowsey finishes 3-pointer after contact
